OL,3,CSouthampton NHS trust facing multi-
OL,4,Cmillion pound deficit
OL,6,FOne of the South's biggest hospitals
OL,7,Fis currently facing a multi-million
OL,8,Fpound deficit, a report has shown.
OL,10,FUniversity Hospital Southampton (UHS)
OL,11,Fruns Southampton General Hospital, one
OL,12,Fof England's leading facilities.
OL,14,FIn its latest board meeting, the trust
OL,15,Freported a monthly 'underlying
OL,16,Fdeficit' of #6.1million, a
OL,17,Fdeterioration on 2023, where the
OL,18,Fdeficit averaged between #4-4.5million
OL,19,Fper month.
