OL,3,CSouthampton NHS trust facing multi-
OL,4,Cmillion pound deficit
OL,6,FThis increase has been blamed on 'real-
OL,7,Fterms funding cuts' in the overall
OL,8,Fallocation of money to UHS.
OL,10,FThe report says the NHS trust is under-
OL,11,Ffunded on its contract with Hampshire
OL,12,Fand Isle of Wight Integrated Care
OL,13,FBoard by #33million.
OL,15,FIt blames a growth in the number of
OL,16,Fpatients for this, as well as
OL,17,Finflation putting pressure on its
OL,18,Fexisting funding.
