OL,3,CSouthampton NHS trust facing multi-
OL,4,Cmillion pound deficit
OL,6,FA shortfall in 'additional funding'
OL,7,Ffor 'nationally negotiated pay awards'
OL,8,Fhas also been noted as a 'driver' for
OL,9,Fthe deficit.
OL,11,FIncrease in energy bills and high-cost
OL,12,Fdrugs spend were also highlighted,
OL,13,Fwith drug spending said to be
OL,14,F'significantly' above what is
OL,15,Fcurrently funded.
OL,17,FIn the report, UHS says it is
OL,18,F'continuing to raise' its financial
OL,19,Fpressures with commissioners, and it
OL,20,Fhopes to find a 'resolution' in the
OL,21,Ffuture.
