OL,3,CSouthampton NHS trust facing multi-
OL,4,Cmillion pound deficit
OL,6,FIt ended 2023 with cash reserves of
OL,7,F#79million, which has reduced to
OL,8,F#57million by April 2024.
OL,10,FThe trust says it is also applying
OL,11,Fadditional vigilance to assess ongoing
OL,12,Fviability of the capital programme,
OL,13,Fand will also ensure the NHS England
OL,14,Fdraw down process 'is ready if and
OL,15,Fwhen required'.
